{"type":"message","id":"4a3e7dde","parentId":"f7c87ee4","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:30:58.940Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rco9qo4axjfl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type { OpenClawPluginApi } from \"openclaw/plugin-sdk\";\nimport { sendGreetings, type GreetingConfig } from \"./src/greeting.js\";\n\nconst plugin = {\n  id: \"feishu-greeting\",\n  name: \"Feishu Greeting\",\n  description: \"Auto-send opening messages to Feishu users on gateway startup\",\n  configSchema: { type: \"object\" as const },\n  register(api: OpenClawPluginApi) {\n    const config = api.pluginConfig as GreetingConfig | undefined;\n    if (!config?.message) {\n      api.logger.debug(\"feishu-greeting: no message configured, skipping\");\n      return;\n    }\n    if (!config.targets || config.targets.length === 0) {\n      api.logger.debug(\"feishu-greeting: no targets configured, skipping\");\n      return;\n    }\n\n    api.on(\"gateway_start\", async () => {\n      try {\n        await sendGreetings({ api, config });\n      } catch (err) {\n        api.logger.warn(`feishu-greeting: failed: ${String(err)}`);\n      }\n    });\n  },\n};\n\nexport default plugin;\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773307858936}}
{"type":"message","id":"43938836","parentId":"4a3e7dde","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:31:12.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the problem now. The feishu-greeting plugin imports from \"../../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\" but the relative path doesn't resolve correctly because the plugins are installed in different directories.\n\nThe simplest fix would be to:\n1. Check if there's a way to use node module resolution\n2. Or copy the needed functions\n\nActually, looking at the directory structure:\n- /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-greeting/\n- /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/\n\nSo from feishu-greeting, ../../feishu-openclaw-plugin would go to /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/../../ which is wrong.\n\nWait, let me re-check:\n- /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-greeting/\n- Going up 2 levels from here would be /home/gem/workspace/agent/\n- Then feishu-openclaw-plugin would be /home/gem/workspace/agent/feishu-openclaw-plugin/\n\nBut the actual path is /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/\n\nSo the import path is wrong. It should be \"../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\" not \"../../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\".\n\nBut wait, this plugin was working before. Let me think about this more carefully. The plugin was installed, but maybe after the update, something changed. Actually, looking at the error again:\n\n```\n[plugins] feishu-greeting failed to load from /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-greeting/index.ts: Error: Cannot find module '../../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js'\n```\n\nThe path \"../../feishu-openclaw-plugin\" from /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-greeting/ would resolve to:\n\n\n- /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/ (1 level up)\n- /home/gem/workspace/agent/ (2 levels up)\n- Then feishu-openclaw-plugin would be /home/gem/workspace/agent/feishu-openclaw-plugin\n\nBut that's wrong because the actual directory is /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin. The correct import should be \"../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\" to stay within the extensions folder.\n\nThe path had the wrong number of directory traversals. I need to fix the import statement to use \"../\" instead of \"../../\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"问题在于导入路径错误。让我修复它：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a1r5p95yg207_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-greeting/src/greeting.ts","new_string":"// 依赖 feishu-openclaw-plugin\nimport { sendMessageFeishu } from \"../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\";\nimport { normalizeFeishuTarget } from \"../feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/core/targets.js\";","old_string":"// 依赖 feishu-openclaw-plugin\nimport { sendMessageFeishu } from \"../../feishu-openclaw-plugin/index.js\";\nimport { normalizeFeishuTarget } from \"../../feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/core/targets.js\";"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":496,"output":704,"cacheRead":39421,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773307858940}}
